<h2>Concept</h2>
<p>
Multiple autonomous sound layers create a spatial rainforest:
rain, forest floor, monkeys, birds, insects, macaw, distant bells.
The function <code>forest_voice</code> simulates distance through filtering and amplitude reduction.
